I reviewed the telemetry and reasoning: trace anomalies at MG01 (traffic drops and duration/p95 increases) started at 2021-03-09 09:52:00 (UTC+8), followed ~1.5 minutes later by an error-log burst on apache02/apache01 at 09:53:26–09:53:42. The temporal order, magnitude of traffic drop (well below global p5), and correlated downstream errors indicate MG01 experienced a network-level disruption that propagated to downstream services.

